# Approach
Identify the sorted half from the array, pickup the smallest element from that half, update the answer if it is smaller than the answer, then eliminate that half. Repeat this until the search space gets exhausted.

# Complexity
- Time complexity:
O(log(n))

- Space complexity:
O(1)

# C++ Code
